  "circuit": {
    "name": "SAR ADC 4-bit (DSL spike)",
    "description": "4-bit SAR ADC: VIN → comparator → SAR write-gate → 4× D-FF → R-2R DAC → comparator (feedback). 2-bit down-counter sequences MSB→LSB. Generated from inline DSL spec; subcircuits are interface-only stubs.",
